title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jan 31 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jan 31 2022
description:
Adam Carolla tells Clay & Buck how we fight cancel culture, and he notes, "I've learned nothing about how viruses work in the last two years, but I learned everything about how government works." Psaki mocks the concept of "Soft on Crime." Trump stands up for Canadian truckers, Trudeau trashes them, praises BLM. Dwarf actors bash Peter Dinklage over Snow White criticism. C&B take calls on Canadian freedom convoy.
